Yeah but aren't they all really ugly??

Mary B




not any more!! the old reputation doesn't apply anymore; they've gone
fashionable trying to capture other markets besides old hippies and people
with bad feet...

check out styles here: www.Birkenstock-cn.com . specials, bargains and
closeouts here, too.

for even better prices, look for them on ebay; lots of new but obsolete
(past seasons) styles, plus sometimes gently used ones. best to find them
locally to try on to figure out your sizing, then buy online.
